description: This common Parvati purrs with a rating of 83, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 83, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 1 for East, 2 for South, and Leverage for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [83 Votes, Common]
